{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Auz wiſſa Galwâ/ ne taupi/ pazell tawu Bal- fi ka Basuni/ un pa- ſtuddina manneem Lauditin fa- ruu Pahrkahpschannu/ un tam Jehkaba Namman ſawus Greb- kus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tee mekle mannis ikdee- naſ/ itt ka buhtu teem labs Prahts pee tahs Atſihſchanaſ mannu Zettu/ ka Laudis/ kas Taitnibu darrifschi/ un to Tee- fu ſawa Deewa ne atstahj. Tee waiza man to Teesu tahs Taiſ- nibas/ un grib klaht pee Deewa nahkt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kapebz (fakka tee) gawe- jam mehs/ un tu to ne uslub- ko? kapebz mehrdejam mehs fe- wis/ un tu ne gribbi to finnaht? raugi/ tai Deena/ kad juhs ga- wejat/ tad dsennat juhs ſawas Rahribas/ un plehſchat wiſſu ſawu Paradu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Redſi/ juhs gawejaſ/ ka juhs barratees un reijatees/ un beſdeewigi ar Dubri fittat. Ne gavejeet ta ka taggad/ ka juhs ſawn Balsi Augſtibâ leekat dsirdeht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Buhtu tas tahda Gaue- ſhana ko es eeredsu/ ka tas Zil- weks ſewi kahdu Deenu mehrde/ jeb ſawnGalwu nokar ka Aſchu- Stohbri/ jeb weenu Maisu jeb Peluns appaksch ſew bahrsta? Woj juhs to weenu Gaueſchannu notanzt/ un weenu tam KUN- GAM patibkamm Deenu?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Neggi tas irr weena Ga-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "weschana/ ko es eeredsu/ atraiſi/ ko tu ar Besdeeuibu eſſi febjts/ raifi wahta to Juhgu pee teem/ ko tu ſpaids/ atlaid fwabbadus tohs/ kam tu gruhti darri/ un atjeun wiſſadu Nastu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Neggi tas ta peederr/ ka tu tam Iſfalkufchaim tawu Mai- ſi laus/ un tohs nabbagus Iſ- dsichtus Manuna eewedd/ kad tu weenu Railu eereds/ka tu win- nu apfeds/ un ne apſleppeeß no tawas Meesas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad anſihs tawa Gaifina ka tas Anſeklis/ un tawa Dsee- dinaschana ahtri iſplauks/ un tawa Taitniba ees tawa Breeſ- châ/ un ta KUNGA Sohdiba tewi pawaddihe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fanſſi tu/ un tas KUNGS atbildihs/ tu brcheſti/ un wiſch fazzihs: Redſi/ ſche es efimu. Ja tu no tawa Widdus atxeemi to Nastu/ to Rahdicha- nu ar Pirkſteem/ un to netaifau Wallodu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ja tu tam Iſfalku- fcham atdarrifi tawu Sirdi/ un to apbehdinatu Dwehfeli pee-ehe- dinati/ tad uſecs tawa Gaifina Tumsibâ/ un tawa Pakrehſliba buhs ka Deenas-Widdus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS wad- diths tewi bes Mitteſchanae/ un pee-ehehdinahs tawu Dwehfeli Bullu Laikâ/ un ſtiprinahs ta- wusRaulns.Un tu buhſi kaſlap- vinachts Dahrs/ un ka Uhdens Awots/ kam Uhdens ne truheſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kas no tewim (d|ims)/ M 2 tee\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
